Annotation Type FieldBuilder.CheckBox


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
@Documented
public static @interface FieldBuilder.CheckBox
    Specifies how a Java property should be edited in Vaadin using an CheckBox.
    See Also:
    FieldBuilder.AbstractField, FieldBuilder
